The '''Armenia national under-17 football team''' is the youth football team of [[Armenia]]. The team is based mostly on the young players from the league and competes every years in order to qualify for the [[European Under-17 Football Championship]]. The team played its first match in 1993, Armenia having until 1992 been part of the [[USSR]].
